attributionInfo.brokerName: Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate
Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate

data.description: Beautifully updated throughout! Ranch home located in a cul-de-sac. Custom features include archways, crown molding, white colonist doors, & upgraded trim. Wood laminate floors. Recessed lighting. Inviting entry with front porch. Bright living room. Separate dining room that leads out to the backyard. Updated open kitchen featuring breakfast bar, cherry cabinets, granite countertops, SS appliances (new stove 2022) (new D/W 2023), tiled backsplash, & pantry. Huge family room with 1/2 bath. All the bathrooms have been updated. Three spacious bedrooms. Primary bedroom with double closets & private bathroom with walk-in shower. Newer windows (7 years old). New vinyl siding & gutters (2 years old). You are going to love relaxing in the fenced-in backyard featuring epoxy patio & a brick paver patio. Newer shed with loft storage. Garage with epoxy flooring. Award winning school district 54 & 211. Walking distance to the park. Just move right into this gorgeous home!
